Download the Ubuntu VM from the following link. This URL takes you to a webpage with a link to download the file.
https://utdallas.box.com/ubuntu-minimal-emu

Alternatively, you can use this direct link:
https://utdallas.box.com/shared/static/uu2c4oacezanzczjrkqtl6w9tsq6il8g.xz

Extract the image after downloading using tar as follows:
tar xvf <archive name>
